variable C4${dir} equal 0.5*(${C4neg}+${C4pos})
variable C44 equal 0.5*(${C4neg}+${C4pos})
variable C44 equal 0.5*(31.5962361543902+${C4pos})
variable C44 equal 0.5*(31.5962361543902+31.5962361499497)
variable C5${dir} equal 0.5*(${C5neg}+${C5pos})
variable C54 equal 0.5*(${C5neg}+${C5pos})
variable C54 equal 0.5*(5.24375117263702e-10+${C5pos})
